turnkey-mastodon-19.0 (1) turnkey; urgency=low

  * Initial release — Mastodon v4.5.8 federated social network

  * Ruby 3.4.7 via rbenv (common ruby vertical, jemalloc enabled)

  * Node.js 20 LTS via n (common nodejs vertical)

  * PostgreSQL backend (common pgsql vertical)

  * Redis for caching and Sidekiq (common redis vertical)

  * Nginx reverse proxy with WebSocket support for streaming API

  * IPv6-first upstream blocks (::1)

  * Systemd services: mastodon-web, mastodon-sidekiq, mastodon-streaming

  * Firstboot inithook: domain, admin email, admin password

  * mastodon-upgrade helper for in-place version upgrades

  * Built on TurnKey common verticals — no duplicated Ruby/Node setup

 -- Marcos Mendez <m@pop.coop>  Wed, 25 Mar 2026 00:00:00 -0300
